Each faction in Twilight Imperium has access to exclusive technologies that can be researched in addition to the general technologies available to all factions.

This list does not contain [[Discordant Stars Faction Specific Units (UNOFFICIAL)|Discordant Stars unit upgrade technologies]].


==[[Shipwrights of Axis (UNOFFICIAL)|The Shipwrights of Axis]]==
{{Tech|propulsion}}  '''<big>Rift Engines</big>'''<blockquote>After you [[Activation|activate]] a system, you may [[Readied and Exhausted|exhaust]] this card to choose 1 [[Units#Ships|ship]] you control and roll a die. On a result of 1-3, remove that [[Units#Ships|ship]] from the game board; on a result of 4-10, apply +2 to that ship’s move value during this [[Tactical Action|tactical action]].</blockquote><blockquote>Prerequisites: {{Tech|propulsion}}</blockquote>{{Tech|cybernetic}}  '''<big>Emergency Deployment</big>'''<blockquote>ACTION: [[Readied and Exhausted|Exhaust]] this card to place or move 1 of your [[Space Dock|space docks]] onto a [[Planets and Systems|planet]] you control.</blockquote><blockquote>Prerequisites: {{Tech|cybernetic}}{{Tech|cybernetic}}{{Tech|cybernetic}}</blockquote>

