==[[Edyn Mandate (UNOFFICIAL)|The Edyn Mandate]]==
{{Tech|biotic}}  '''<big>Unity Algorithm</big>'''<blockquote>Once per [[Agenda Phase|agenda phase]], after an [[Agenda Cards|agenda]] is [[Agenda Phase#Reveal%20First%20Agenda|revealed]], you may predict aloud an outcome of that [[Agenda Cards|agenda]].

